{"tid":665294,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（徬徨）唔見咗啲抗抑鬱藥，點算好","createTime":"2018-05-14T22:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T10:38:25.000Z","uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a26e57ae0cde922f927c0d8a4695b00b1dd29376","tid":665294,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T22:24:18.000Z","msg":"我有啲懷疑係俾食大麻嘅roommate偷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身我食緊隻藥食埋大麻會仲high(上網睇番嚟)<br />\n但係我又唔敢問佢，因為本身同佢幾friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又衰，尋晚凌晨三點幾先番hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煮左飯之後攞埋成盒藥出廳<br />\n嗰晚真係好攰，而我又真係唔記得有冇留咗喺廳<br />\n不過我今晚喺自己間房就搵唔倒啲藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪俾人攞咗都無所謂<br />\n我最擔心嘅係醫生唔肯開過俾我(我兩個禮拜之後先複診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"50cc8ecbf5cdc5498d4e5c4367bfdd78e9f6e28f","tid":665294,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T22:24:45.000Z","msg":"我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e0304f98ea89246f96f1f95d6f80569007b8ef","tid":665294,"uid":174919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T22:25:47.000Z","msg":"打去診所問咗先，解釋清楚件事"},{"pid":"4e781077e00f551c1b31c62c095da64c97824f3a","tid":665294,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T22:25:52.000Z","msg":"唔記得講番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喺英國讀書"},{"pid":"d2655d66ff84e9c89bfdc945191f7d9eb6c34d4c","tid":665294,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e0304f98ea89246f96f1f95d6f80569007b8ef","tid":665294,"uid":174919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T22:25:47.000Z","msg":